    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dual Combat</i> is a quirky puzzle-action game, where you must defeat an enemy that copies your every move. Are you smart enough to outsmart yourself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/8922c340ddb42a486e7db021afd5640f.webp?t=1769803238\" width=399 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite disagreeing on which pancake topping is the best, the Raspberry and Blueberry armies have lived together in peace. That is until the Blueberries' beloved pancake chef is kidnapped! Journey across enemy lines to rescue Chef Lupe and save the Weekend Pancake Brunch from being cancelled.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/cef4fab66a0df6eb57445df542e5b156.webp?t=1769803238\" width=223 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“For every action there is an equal and opposite reaction.”</i> - <i>Some guy named Isaac</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Dual Combat</i> the player controls both soldiers synchronously, meaning that for every action you perform the enemy performs it too. Use this to your advantage as you expose your enemy on the battlefield and knock them out, but watch out - one wrong move and it's game over <i>for you</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/728da2ac4706ccfed680a737c15e374e.poster.avif?t=1769803238\" width=616 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/728da2ac4706ccfed680a737c15e374e.webm?t=1769803238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/728da2ac4706ccfed680a737c15e374e.mp4?t=1769803238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/5f6dfb73ea3137fb3b3a4c415c1c4150.webp?t=1769803238\" width=278 height=30 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast, punch, and “block” your way across Nomansland as you conquer various puzzles using unique weapons and objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/ac5fd6d742558fc32e67029f8681e1d8.poster.avif?t=1769803238\" width=616 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/ac5fd6d742558fc32e67029f8681e1d8.webm?t=1769803238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/ac5fd6d742558fc32e67029f8681e1d8.mp4?t=1769803238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/db0fa7b40ebcfd5e0f6fceb184c7865c.webp?t=1769803238\" width=184 height=30 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock fun cosmetics as you progress through the game and complete special challenges. You may not always win, but at least you can go down in style! 💅✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/852b5f857cfbbab85d6034c56d5bfebf.poster.avif?t=1769803238\" width=616 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/852b5f857cfbbab85d6034c56d5bfebf.webm?t=1769803238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200620/extras/852b5f857cfbbab85d6034c56d5bfebf.mp4?t=1769803238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
